715090f-a.title: Manhattan: 114th Street (West) - 8th Avenue
715090f-a.text:
West 114th Street, west from Eighth to Morningside Aves., showing
the street surface being relaid to Manhattan Ave. On the west stde of
Morningside Ave. is Morningside Park; a hilly incline, atop which appears
Notre Dame Chapel (right) and a portion of St. Lukes Hospital (left).
October 8, 1936.
W.P.A. Photo.
Federal Art Project.
CREDIT LINE IMPERATIVE ON ALL REPRODUCTIONS.
